{"tid":1758320,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣藝人高以翔拍攝大陸綜藝《追我吧》猝死 終年35歲","createTime":"2019-11-27T03:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T04:46:26.000Z","uid":67294,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"24adea0b074eeb962d88eb1dbcc5d643ac4630be","tid":1758320,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/W7maQ78JXeLJrv1KO_smSg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/ebc.net.tw/9f6bcd0f8f33e3eb7db86923d6fa3aa6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FW7maQ78JXeLJrv1KO_smSg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Febc.net.tw%2F9f6bcd0f8f33e3eb7db86923d6fa3aa6&h=541390c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20191127/1669245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20191127%2F1669245%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=dde183a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20191127%2F1669245%2F&h=2d142e9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20191127/1669245/</a><br />\n<br />\n35歲男星高以翔高大帥氣，在對岸演藝圈發展順遂，最近才出席金雞奬頒奬典禮，但今凌晨3點多微博網友爆出他在錄中國綜藝節目《追我吧》暈倒昏迷，「現場的人一直在喊有沒有心跳，心肺復甦做了3分鐘都沒有醒來」，並說情況嚴重，補充表示「心臟停了3分鐘，心肺復甦15分鐘，有心跳了，現在送醫院了」，消息傳開後，網友都為高以翔集氣盼他度過難關。據悉，高以翔的友人接到噩耗後狂哭。中國官煤《浙江新聞》證實「本端證實高以翔搶救無效去世。」中國媒體《今日頭條》也引述《浙江新聞》報導高以翔不幸的消息。<br />\n<br />\n傳高以翔是在錄浙江衛視《追我吧》節目時發生意外，這節目是拼體力的競技節目，宗旨是在你追我逃的比賽氛圍中突破體能極限，但現在卻出了意外，節目固定來賓有范冰冰的弟弟范丞丞、陳偉霆、黃景瑜及宋祖兒，而高以翔做為特別來賓來錄新的一集。<br />\n<br />\n35歲高以翔是加拿大籍，出生台北，在溫哥華長大，2005年來台發展，2006年從電視劇配角出道，但讓他成名的是跟丁春誠、藍鈞天、陳紹誠組成的「時尚F4」，身高193公分的他高大英挺最受矚目，曾入選世界百大帥哥第55名，2016年美國網站「TC Candler」公布當年「世界最美臉蛋」時，他便攻占第7名。<br />\n<br />\n高以翔轉戰中國影視圈多年，接拍多部電影及戲劇，曾接拍好萊塢電影《天使聖物：骸骨之城》，2年前拍《遇見王瀝川》時有了「新國民老公」稱號，去年跟舒淇、鹿晗合作科幻電影《上海堡壘》扮帥氣指揮官，還特地減重5公斤，透露「演軍人一直是自己的夢想」。"},{"pid":"f2995bc65b5c314155e8bcaca7237b79040a2e87","tid":1758320,"uid":47223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:33:48.000Z","msg":"痴埋大陸?"},{"pid":"342ede20eabe8fa35c3a23e46f38e82b35c37cfc","tid":1758320,"uid":403,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"鼠疫定猝死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12898d05565a3c53bf6a20d4d7ac97f451841e1b","tid":1758320,"uid":77948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:34:18.000Z","msg":"陳偉霆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時到佢"},{"pid":"7f4c7503bd3e2b5d392cd3bf2b1255b7fd69a199","tid":1758320,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4669baf21eee55bdb649b58f248c16c1d97532d2","tid":1758320,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"342ede20eabe8fa35c3a23e46f38e82b35c37cfc","tid":1758320,"uid":403,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"鼠疫定猝死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"鼠疫應該唔止佢一個，睇落去"},{"pid":"901b0f6181ca1c4888806ec59f8be374119c9fa3","tid":1758320,"uid":36058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12898d05565a3c53b